headline: Can Nvidia's Jensen Huang Beat This Latest Challenge? Here's What History Says.
summary: Nvidia (NASDAQ: NVDA) stock may have been at the top of the world a few months ago -- but these days, it's been wallowing in the doldrums.  Fellow tech and growth stocks have tumbled in recent weeks amid concern about President Trump's tariffs on imports.  The idea is these taxes may increase costs for companies such as Nvidia that produce products abroad -- and a general increase in prices may hurt the overall economy.
